{"tid":19792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"放底你既童年陰影","createTime":"2016-12-03T04:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T14:41:00.000Z","uid":48878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24aa644142dc190d3a4cbeff3abed244e1ea9733","tid":19792,"uid":48878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:03:54.000Z","msg":"[img]細細個有次腸胃炎 入左醫院 個醫生哥哥塞左粒藥丸仔入屎眼到<br />\n之後D屎好似S風暴咁湧埋黎 拿拿聲去痾屎 點知廁所排緊隊個姐姐講左句 嘩屌 好臭啊,有冇搞錯<br />\n自從個日開始 我就冇試過係屋企以外既廁所痾屎... <br />\n直到依家我忍左廿幾年, 都係會番到屋企先痾 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近幾年 我慢慢放底自尊 <br />\n真係頂唔撚住要出黎時, 我都會痾左面個浸<br />\n痾完一條就沖一次水<br />\n終於解決左臭味既問題<br />\n底個浸留番屋企慢慢痾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2dc53a1aca084b927a45f28e1d3f4749ec94331","tid":19792,"uid":45142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:06:21.000Z","msg":"10歲睇鹹片電腦中毒比屋企人發現"},{"pid":"4bbf7f0c962b1af65a3969b4c64be3c3df665da6","tid":19792,"uid":5751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"睇打屁"},{"pid":"31f601e59b439b8775054cf92a65a39f2e8602de","tid":19792,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:29:22.000Z","msg":"唔再鍾意女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4c931657d62a6ab389dd8a66a93e16fe3b49ac","tid":19792,"uid":39463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:35:51.000Z","msg":"成個童年都係陰影<br />\n令你唔相信親人一定會對你好，只有自己可以相信"},{"pid":"e7e9ef6c242e39ab88e078313be5f22f3cc69764","tid":19792,"uid":8534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:37:51.000Z","msg":"小丑"},{"pid":"b081d25964fb3b1bad2b53a4740eb756cba92c7f","tid":19792,"uid":1928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:38:39.000Z","msg":"好似 無"},{"pid":"8430b8e7fda1e19cf8c14ea1cdd2f8e6d6d49f77","tid":19792,"uid":28726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:43:36.000Z","msg":"本身小學畢業典禮搵我上去講致謝詞<br />\n我寫咗好耐 仲練埋<br />\n無啦啦有日老師同我講 俾另一個男仔講<br />\n原因係我有其他表演 應該俾啲機會人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁等於幫人寫埋稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e365ce0d5bd82b5284f3de49e2f6d2306549e71","tid":19792,"uid":30910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:45:59.000Z","msg":"唔算童年陰影<br />\n不過細個成日發同一個惡夢<br />\n我細個係訓上格床既<br />\n夢入面床同門中間變左深淵同勁遠距離<br />\n落唔一個床同勁淆 淆足成個夢<br />\n依家諗番都覺得好恐怖"},{"pid":"e7bd58889c952b2ebba43450bf5b5aafacf8d201","tid":19792,"uid":45276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:48:24.000Z","msg":"屋企3個老母 日日係到計算大家 <br />\n但見親面都好撚和諧 <br />\n令我基本上唔相信女人所有野 <br />\n連中學借功課抄 迫不得已要借女仔個份抄<br />\n 借完都會問個男仔黎對答案 <br />\n出到黎做野 女上司d命令都係半信半疑 <br />\n要問多次男上司先會放心<br />\n所以決定做地盤算。冇女人 爽<br />\n<br />\n申利 唔係基佬 會j囡囡 只係打從心底唔相信佢地"},{"pid":"738f8318ee8cb328cfcf1353efb9e4cd44ab6282","tid":19792,"uid":50432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:48:58.000Z","msg":"6歲時被隔離屋12歲中一女生捉入廁所，被逼揸佢個飛機場，搞到而家淫底加巨乳控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce43d108e73c18a663cdf343443a1d538159d9e","tid":19792,"uid":5749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:49:33.000Z","msg":"細個嘅時候老母租左隻怪談（大頭怪嬰）返黎睇<br />\n嚇撚到我發咗幾年惡夢都關大頭怪嬰事"},{"pid":"d51bd3271224950637ef66808b44ecd469ff64e0","tid":19792,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:50:06.000Z","msg":"細個食過皮蛋然後嘔到仆街<br />\n<br />\n自此唔敢再食"},{"pid":"72198e411b6ece75f99ec3f8fa8ec6b13b95a274","tid":19792,"uid":48878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:31:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成個童年都係陰影<br />\n令你唔相信親人一定會對你好，只有自己可以相信</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細細個已經識諗呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c9b00cc1c17cf65bccbe5333f0d2c6f9d69d73","tid":19792,"uid":48878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:31:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個食過皮蛋然後嘔到仆街<br />\n<br />\n自此唔敢再食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 我都試過 皮蛋真係唔好亂試"},{"pid":"93b33167c70f3e837c5a5bbea3e71e2a6daaf543","tid":19792,"uid":48878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個嘅時候老母租左隻怪談（大頭怪嬰）返黎睇<br />\n嚇撚到我發咗幾年惡夢都關大頭怪嬰事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  細膽到連回魂夜都淆到仆街"},{"pid":"b5f56bb54d1b3ee0837e8211bcebe448e7d25a76","tid":19792,"uid":48878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6歲時被隔離屋12歲中一女生捉入廁所，被逼揸佢個飛機場，搞到而家淫底加巨乳控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢個光影黎"},{"pid":"dc6f986d4ac6f6faa89a9c990e3c1dece8203ba0","tid":19792,"uid":48878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:34:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企3個老母 日日係到計算大家 <br />\n但見親面都好撚和諧 <br />\n令我基本上唔相信女人所有野 <br />\n連中學借功課抄 迫不得已要借女仔個份抄<br />\n 借完都會問個男仔黎對答案 <br />\n出到黎做野 女上司d命令都係半信半疑 <br />\n要問多次男上司先會放心<br />\n所以決定做地盤算。冇女人 爽<br />\n<br />\n申利 唔係基佬 會j囡囡 只係打從心底唔相信佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難搵另一半 巴打 放鬆啲"},{"pid":"e0726bdfe9272202bb1f3bc03b54bf40c7438ff1","tid":19792,"uid":48878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:34:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔算童年陰影<br />\n不過細個成日發同一個惡夢<br />\n我細個係訓上格床既<br />\n夢入面床同門中間變左深淵同勁遠距離<br />\n落唔一個床同勁淆 淆足成個夢<br />\n依家諗番都覺得好恐怖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過細細個發同一個夢 跳落山"},{"pid":"24cfc2927ed801ce3a5ccf602e8e4ec9d0de9c85","tid":19792,"uid":48878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身小學畢業典禮搵我上去講致謝詞<br />\n我寫咗好耐 仲練埋<br />\n無啦啦有日老師同我講 俾另一個男仔講<br />\n原因係我有其他表演 應該俾啲機會人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁等於幫人寫埋稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n陰影呢?"},{"pid":"c8a422b8ed3c7fff4416bc215dc301cc5ba32692","tid":19792,"uid":48878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔再鍾意女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHow about 摸女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3a53d425a26d552f76ef6cfea33387f9b9706a","tid":19792,"uid":48878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇打屁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜撚野黎?"},{"pid":"e03e19b2e01ab9ecdce186d4177da065f5fa5a00","tid":19792,"uid":2869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6歲時被隔離屋12歲中一女生捉入廁所，被逼揸佢個飛機場，搞到而家淫底加巨乳控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}